#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, no-wrap
msgid "Defining entities in external projects or jars"
msgstr "在外部项目或jar中定义实体"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hibernate ORM in Quarkus relies on compile-time bytecode enhancements to your entities. If you define your entities in the\n"
"same project where you build your Quarkus application, everything will work fine."
msgstr "Quarkus 中的 Hibernate ORM 依赖于对实体进行的编译时字节码增强。如果你在构建 Quarkus 应用程序的同一项目中定义实体，一切都会正常运行。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If the entities come from external projects\n"
"or jars, you can make sure that your jar is treated like a Quarkus application library by adding an empty `META-INF/beans.xml` file."
msgstr "如果这些实体来自外部项目或 JAR 文件，您可以通过添加一个空的 `META-INF/beans.xml` 文件，确保您的 JAR 文件被视为 Quarkus 应用程序库。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This will allow Quarkus to index and enhance your entities as if they were inside the current project."
msgstr "这样，Quarkus 就能像这些实体位于当前项目中一样，对其进行索引和增强。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Hibernate ORM in development mode"
msgstr "开发模式下的 Hibernate ORM"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"During tests and in xref:dev-mode-differences.adoc[development mode], Hibernate ORM benefits from xref:datasource.adoc#dev-services[datasource Dev Services],\n"
"making configuration of database connections unnecessary."
msgstr "在测试和 xref:dev-mode-differences.adoc[开发模式] 下，Hibernate ORM 可借助 xref:datasource.adoc#dev-services[数据源开发服务（Dev Services] ），从而无需配置数据库连接。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The main remaining question is how to initialize that database."
msgstr "目前剩下的主要问题是如何初始化该数据库。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The first choice is to use `quarkus.hibernate-orm.schema-management.strategy=drop-and-create` in conjunction with `import.sql`."
msgstr "首选方案是使用 `quarkus.hibernate-orm.schema-management.strategy=drop-and-create` ，并配合 `import.sql` 使用。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"That way for every change to your app and in particular to your entities, the database schema will be properly recreated\n"
"and your data fixture (stored in `import.sql`) will be used to repopulate it from scratch."
msgstr "这样一来，每当对应用程序（尤其是实体）进行修改时，数据库模式都会被正确重建，并且会使用您的数据 fixture（存储在 `import.sql` 中）从头开始重新填充数据。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This is best to perfectly control your environment and works magic with Quarkus live reload mode:\n"
"your entity changes or any change to your `import.sql` is immediately picked up and the schema updated without restarting the application!\n"
"In fact, this is the default when using xref:dev-services.adoc[Dev Services]."
msgstr "这是完美控制运行环境的最佳方式，与 Quarkus 的实时重新加载模式配合使用效果尤为出色：实体发生变更或 `import.sql` 文件出现任何更改时，系统都会立即检测到并更新模式，而无需重启应用程序！事实上，在使用 xref:dev-services.adoc[Dev Services] 时，这正是默认行为。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can use a file with a different name than `import.sql` by setting the property `quarkus.hibernate-orm.sql-load-script` in `application.properties`.\n"
"You can also provide a `.zip` file in the same way which should contain only the files containing the SQL statements to be executed."
msgstr "您可以通过在 `application.properties` 中设置 `quarkus.hibernate-orm.sql-load-script` 属性，使用名称与 `import.sql` 不同的文件。您还可以通过相同的方式提供一个 `.zip` 文件，该文件中应仅包含待执行的 SQL 语句文件。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The second approach is to use `quarkus.hibernate-orm.schema-management.strategy=update`."
msgstr "第二种方法是使用 `quarkus.hibernate-orm.schema-management.strategy=update` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This approach is best when you do many entity changes but\n"
"still need to work on a copy of the production data\n"
"or if you want to reproduce a bug that is based on specific database entries.\n"
"`update` is a best effort from Hibernate ORM and will fail in specific situations\n"
"including altering your database structure which could lead to data loss.\n"
"For example if you change structures which violate a foreign key constraint, Hibernate ORM might have to bail out.\n"
"But for development, these limitations are acceptable."
msgstr "当您需要对实体进行大量修改，但仍需在生产数据的副本上操作时，或者您希望重现基于特定数据库条目的错误时，这种方法最为合适。Hibernate ORM 的 `update 操作` 仅尽最大努力，在某些特定情况下（包括修改数据库结构）可能会失败，这可能导致数据丢失。 例如，如果您修改的数据结构违反了外键约束，Hibernate ORM 可能不得不中止操作。但在开发过程中，这些限制是可以接受的。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The third approach is to use `quarkus.hibernate-orm.schema-management.strategy=none`."
msgstr "第三种方法是使用 `quarkus.hibernate-orm.schema-management.strategy=none` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This approach is best when you are working on a copy of the production data but want to fully control the schema evolution.\n"
"Or if you use a database schema migration tool like xref:flyway.adoc[Flyway] or xref:liquibase.adoc[Liquibase]."
msgstr "当你正在处理生产数据的副本，但希望完全掌控模式演变时，这种方法最为合适。或者，如果你使用 xref:flyway.adoc[Flyway] 或 xref:liquibase.adoc[Liquibase] 这样的数据库模式迁移工具时，也适用这种方法。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"With this approach when making changes to an entity, make sure to adapt the database schema accordingly;\n"
"you could also use `validate` to have Hibernate verify the schema matches its expectations."
msgstr "采用这种方法时，在对实体进行修改后，请务必相应地调整数据库模式；您还可以使用 `validate` 方法，让 Hibernate 验证模式是否符合其预期。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Do not set `quarkus.hibernate-orm.schema-management.strategy` to `drop-and-create` or `update` in your production environment."
msgstr "请勿在生产环境中将 `quarkus.hibernate-orm.schema-management.strategy` 设置为 `drop-and-create` 或 `update` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"These approaches become really powerful when combined with Quarkus configuration profiles.\n"
"You can define different xref:config-reference.adoc#profiles[configuration profiles]\n"
"to select different behaviors depending on your environment.\n"
"This is great because you can define different combinations of Hibernate ORM properties matching the development style you currently need."
msgstr "这些方法与 Quarkus 配置配置文件结合使用时，效果尤为显著。您可以定义不同的 xref:config-reference.adoc#profiles[配置配置文件] ，以便根据所处环境选择不同的行为。这非常有用，因为您可以定义不同组合的 Hibernate ORM 属性，以适应您当前所需的开发风格。"

#. type: Block title
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "application.properties"
msgstr "application.properties"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can start dev mode using a custom profile:"
msgstr "您可以使用自定义配置文件启动开发模式："

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
