msgstr "您可以在 `application.properties` 文件中显式覆盖该设置（例如： `%prod.quarkus.hibernate-orm.sql-load-script = import.sql` ），但我们希望您避免在生产环境中意外覆盖数据库配置 :)"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Speaking of, make sure to not drop your database schema in production!\n"
"Add the following in your properties file."
msgstr "说到这个，请务必不要在生产环境中删除数据库模式！请在属性文件中添加以下内容。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Flyway integration"
