#. type: Title ===
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Weight-based eviction"
msgstr "基于权重的驱逐"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For entities with highly variable sizes (e.g., storing JSON data that ranges from a few bytes to\n"
"megabytes), count-based eviction cannot reliably bound memory usage. In these cases, use weight-based\n"
"eviction instead:"
msgstr "对于数据大小波动较大的实体（例如，存储的 JSON 数据大小从几字节到兆字节不等），基于计数的淘汰机制无法可靠地限制内存使用量。在这种情况下，请改用基于权重的淘汰机制："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `maximum-weight` property sets the total weight limit for the cache region. The `weigher-class`\n"
"property specifies a `com.github.benmanes.caffeine.cache.Weigher` implementation that assigns a\n"
"weight to each cache entry:"
msgstr "`“最大权重”` 属性用于设置缓存区域的总权重限制。 `“权重器类”` 属性指定了一个 `com.github.benmanes.caffeine.cache.Weigher` 实现类，该类负责为每个缓存条目分配权重："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
