msgstr "由于 `@NotNull` 约束， `name` 列具有 `非空` 约束；由于 `@Size(max=50)` 约束，该列的值长度限制为 `50` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Since the `value` property in the entity has no constraints, there are no additional constraints in the DDL,\n"
"and the `255` length limit comes from the default `jakarta.persistence.Column#length()`."
msgstr "由于实体中的 `值` 属性没有约束，因此 DDL 中没有额外的约束， `255 的` 长度限制来自默认的 `jakarta.persistence.Column#length()` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "With the `callback` mode, expect getting a `jakarta.validation.ConstraintViolationException` thrown:"
msgstr "在 `回调` 模式下，预计会抛出一个 `jakarta.validation.ConstraintViolationException 异常` ："

#. type: Plain text
